Title: Single-metric dashlets and metric views: Fix scaling issues
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: metrics
Date: 1683293431
Edition: cee
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.3.0b1

The single-metric dashlets had scaling issues when displaying historic values for certain metrics,
in particular for filesystem metrics such as the filesystem size. This issue also affected the view
columns `Services: Metric History` and `Services: Metric Forecast`.
